BugSquad edit: bug is still present in 2.0 alpha b2f9acb8c96aed0505cbac21661e21e4acef710f
The following script makes the game exit and no error is shown in the dubugger or on the commandline.

```
extends Spatial

class Test:
    func _init():
        pass

func _ready():
    var t = Test.new(1)
```

At core/color.cpp, line 164,

```
void Color::invert() {
  r=1.0-r;
  g=1.0-g;  
  g=1.0-b;  
}
```

should be "b=1.0-b;"
